OL,3,CNew MSPs arrive at Holyrood following
OL,4,CScottish Election
OL,6,FThe South of Scotland's newest MSPs
OL,7,Fhave arrived for their first day at
OL,8,FHolyrood after last week's election.
OL,10,FSome 64 fresh faces will walk the
OL,11,Fhalls of the Edinburgh parliament
OL,12,Ffollowing Friday's results, including
OL,13,F7 new representatives for our region.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/4
