OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1778746039
OL,3,CNew MSPs arrive at Holyrood following
OL,4,CScottish Election
OL,6,FLaura Moodie, who was elected as a
OL,7,FSouth Scotland list MSP for the
OL,8,FScottish Greens, told ITV Border she
OL,9,Fwas 'looking forward to working
OL,10,Fcollaboratively' with other
OL,11,Fpoliticians, and would focus on
OL,12,Fimproving public transport in rural
OL,13,Fareas.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/4
