OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1778746039
OL,3,CNew MSPs arrive at Holyrood following
OL,4,CScottish Election
OL,6,FThe region's three new Reform UK MSPs
OL,7,F- David Kirkwood, Senga Beresford and
OL,8,FJamie Langan - also attended, as did
OL,9,FDuncan Dunlop for the Scottish Liberal
OL,10,FDemocrats, Joe Fagan for Scottish
OL,11,FLabour, and Calum Kerr, who held
OL,12,FMidlothian South, Tweeddale and
OL,13,FLauderdale for the SNP.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
