OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1778746039
OL,3,CNew MSPs arrive at Holyrood following
OL,4,CScottish Election
OL,6,FReturning MSPs, including the Scottish
OL,7,FConservatives' Rachael Hamilton
OL,8,F(Ettrick, Roxburgh and Berwickshire),
OL,9,FCraig Hoy (Dumfriesshire) and Finlay
OL,10,FCarson (Galloway and West Dumfries)
OL,11,Fwill attend the first sitting day of
OL,12,Fthe new parliamentary term on
OL,13,FThursday, along with Scottish Labour
OL,14,Flist MSP Carol Mochan.
OL,16,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,17,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,18,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,19,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,20,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,21,Fbelow...
